rk Post\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Post\"}, {\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C_Spire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"C Spire\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C_Spire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C_Spire\"}, {\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999672018026, \"rank\": 2.0396902807446938e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5704134740246153, \"rank\": 0.7388536312364963, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"C Spire is supportive of our athletes who have worked so hard to be a part of the Olympics,\\\" Hays explained.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C_Spire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"C Spire\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C_Spire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C_Spire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"However, we will not be a part of the offensive and unacceptable mockery of the Last Supper, which is why we are pulling our advertising from the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1345, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mississippi Governor Tate Reeves applauded C Spire's decision while noting, \\\"God will not be mocked.\\\"\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1448, 